   CHENEY-RECORD _ Cursory looks at Dick Cheney's voting record
reveal a very conservative record on certain social issues. But
examining his full record across a broad spectrum illustrates he
was even more of a voice in the wilderness. (Sherman, Atlanta
Journal-Constitution). 25.
</P>
