   BUSINESS
</P>
<P>
   SHAKESPEARE _ We few, we happy few, we band of brothers. It's
not only a well-known line, it's a good business philosophy, says
John Whitney, Columbia U. prof, ex-CEO and part-time PBG resident
who's written a book about business lessons that can be drawn from
the plays of Shakespeare. (Martinez, Palm Beach Post) 28. MOVED.
</P>
